# Job Fetcher Rules

Fetches jobs from boards via APIs or scraping; normalizes to shared domain model.

## Scope
- Board adapter interface and implementations
- Fetch command intake
- Normalization pipeline
- Dedupe by fingerprint
- Fetch run event emission

## Do NOT
- Own user profile CRUD
- Own application submission logic
- Own frontend
- Collapse board logic into controllers

## Conventions
- One adapter per board
- Normalized job DTO contract
- Emit structured events to control service
